@{
  ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<style>
  h1 {
    color: #071952;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
  }

  p,
  ul {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  ul li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  h4 {
    margin-top: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: #246b81;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
  }

  strong {
    color: #37B7C3;
  }
</style>

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>At <strong>User Management App</strong>, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting any personal
  information you share with us.</p>

<h4>Information We Collect</h4>
<p>We may collect basic user details such as username, role, and login credentials to manage user access and permissions
  within the application. This data is used strictly for internal purposes.</p>

<h4>How We Use Your Information</h4>
<ul>
  <li>To authenticate and authorize users</li>
  <li>To manage user roles and access levels</li>
  <li>To improve system performance and user experience</li>
</ul>

<h4>Data Protection</h4>
<p>We implement appropriate security measures to safeguard your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or
  misuse. Your data is not shared with any third party without your consent.</p>

<h4>Cookies and Tracking</h4>
<p>Our application may use cookies or similar technologies to enhance user experience. You can disable cookies through
  your browser settings.</p>

<h4>Changes to This Policy</h4>
<p>We may update our privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be reflected on this page.</p>

<p>If you have any questions or concerns about your privacy, please contact our administrator.</p>
